<p>
<app from="#beg0713002" to="#end0713002"><lem wit="#wit1">佛果</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0713003" to="#end0713003"><lem wit="#wit1">這</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">遮</rdg></app>
<app cb:word-count="247" from="#beg0713004" to="#end0713004"><lem wit="#wit1">頻呼小玉之音<lb n="0713c12" ed="T"/>與檀郎認得之音。然後大唱此音。不數德山<lb n="0713c13" ed="T"/>歌。壓倒雲門曲。凡樓子我若無心之音。及盤<lb n="0713c14" ed="T"/>山紅輪西去之音。皆當立下風。盡是老凍膿。<lb n="0713c15" ed="T"/>所以於建炎中興天子前。奏此一音。四海寂<lb n="0713c16" ed="T"/>默。而無敢鳴。雲居安樂堂上。擅此一音。眾人<lb n="0713c17" ed="T"/>憎嫉。而無敢和。且道。此老子乘誰恩力。得<lb n="0713c18" ed="T"/>恁麼奇特。昔孔子窮於陳蔡之間。左據槁木。<lb n="0713c19" ed="T"/>右擊槁枝而歌。焱氏之風。有其具而無其數。<lb n="0713c20" ed="T"/>有其聲而無宮角。木聲與人聲。犁然有當於<lb n="0713c21" ed="T"/>人之心。乃曰。今之歌者其誰乎。是亦此音。而<lb n="0713c22" ed="T"/>世未之知也。圓悟老師其知之矣。予蚤事佛<lb n="0713c23" ed="T"/>鑑。晚見老師。叩此一音。更無別調。學徒若平<lb n="0713c24" ed="T"/>亦唱師家曲者。集師語要將以刊行。求為序<lb n="0713c25" ed="T"/>篇。以冠卷首。若知此音。則圓悟老師功不浪<lb n="0713c26" ed="T"/>施。若不知</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0713005" to="#end0713005"><lem wit="#wit1">日</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">日太秀居士</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714001" to="#end0714001"><lem wit="#wit1">乃</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">迺</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714002" to="#end0714002"><lem wit="#wit1">咳</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">咏</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714003" to="#end0714003"><lem wit="#wit1">侯</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">侯食邑一千七百戶食實封五百戶</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714005" to="#end0714005"><lem wit="#wit1">佛果</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714006" to="#end0714006"><lem wit="#wit1">師</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">師住成都府崇寧萬壽禪寺</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714007" to="#end0714007"><lem wit="#wit1">卷第一</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714008" to="#end0714008"><lem wit="#wit1">宋</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">住</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714009" to="#end0714009"><lem wit="#wit1">上堂一</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app cb:word-count="10" from="#beg0714010" to="#end0714010"><lem wit="#wit1">住成都府崇寧萬壽禪寺</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0714011" to="#end0714011"><lem wit="#wit1">孤</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">辜</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0716001" to="#end0716001"><lem wit="#wit1">癢</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">痒</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0716002" to="#end0716002"><lem wit="#wit1">進</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">離</rdg></app>
</p>
